references: Amending: Ord 98511, Ord 98755, Ord 94879. Repealing: Ord 101210
summary: An ordinance abolishing the Data Processing Advisory Committee, the Swimming Pool Advisory Committee and the South Seattle Redevelopment Review Committee, whose work has been completed, and repealing Ordinance 101210, Section 3 of Ordinance 98511, Section 2 of Ordinance 98755, and Section 3 of Ordinance 94879.
